| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3913 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0b1ac547-7b35-5894-bb33-b8ddba08fcaa"
